title: #217 - Steve-O
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast we welcome back after 3 long years comedian, stuntman and all around cool dude Steve-O! With him we discuss his new special, Gnarly, which is available at Steveo.com, as well as his animal rights activism, engagement, injuries, and a whole lot more!
